title: Rosie
description: This is actualy a depiction of a tumblr model found at browneyedgummibear.tumblr.com (WARNING, this link is very NSFW). It was painted at a time when I was getting more expressionistic and I sort of wanted to see if I could still paint realistically. In addition I realized I had never actually painted a vagina and felt it was important that I have experience doing that.
